{
  "stem": "3848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then, she started to cry because I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The city's being bombarded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I spoke to my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I told him that mother wants me to stay, and I can't do it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember his words that he told me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He said, son, you're now a grown man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You have to make the decision what you have to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I can't tell you better to stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I would like to have you here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, I knew that I have to go back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I said goodbye to my whole family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this was the last time I saw my family, because I never had another chance to come back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My mother was crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I walked away without turning my head because I had tears in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I didn't want to show them that I'm a boy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I walked about six miles from the city [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the railroad tracks, when I saw a whole group of German planes just flying over my head.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were very low.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I saw them going towards the city of Rowne.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And in a few seconds later, they were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They spread themselves all through the whole city, dropped their bombs, and put the whole city on fire.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I was standing just halfway [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from the city and from my place of work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I couldn't make up my mind what to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I didn't know whether I should run back and see what happened to my family because at 8 o'clock at night, it was already dark.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "You could see the whole city on fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
